Name: STATUS.SFP.ANY_DOWN
Description: reads '1' when any of the enabled SFP ports is down

Name: STATUS.LOCAL_TRIG.CONTINUOUS_ON
Description: continous local L1A on (setup with register 0x1c)

Name: ACTION.RESETS.GENERAL
Description: general reset (ddr3 memory controller not included)

Name: STATUS.SFP_LSC_DOWN_MASK
Description: '1' when DAQLSC of SFP0..2 is down

Name: STATUS.SFP0.SFP_LSC_DOWN_MASK
Description: '1' when DAQLSC of SFP0..2 is down

Name: STATUS.SFP1.SFP_LSC_DOWN_MASK
Description: '1' when DAQLSC of SFP0..2 is down

Name: STATUS.SFP2.SFP_LSC_DOWN_MASK
Description: '1' when DAQLSC of SFP0..2 is down

Name: STATUS.MONITOR_BUFFER.PAGE_NO
Description: SDRAM page number (r/w only when not in run mode)

Name: ACTION.MONITOR_BUFFER.NEXT_PAGE
Description: SDRAM increment page number by 1 in run mode

Name: STATUS.MONITOR_BUFFER.UNREAD_EVENTS
Description: number of unread events captured by monitor

Name: STATUS.MONITOR_BUFFER.WORDS_SFP0
Description: SFP 0 monitored event size in 32-bit word. 0 if no data available

Name: STATUS.MONITOR_BUFFER.WORDS_SFP1
Description: SFP 1 monitored event size in 32-bit word. 0 if no data available

Name: STATUS.MONITOR_BUFFER.WORDS_SFP2
Description: SFP 2 monitored event size in 32-bit word. 0 if no data available

Name: STATUS.FPGA.DIE_TEMP
Description: V6 die temperature in unit of 0.1 degree Celsius

Name: STATUS.TTC.SGL_BIT_ERRORS_LO
Description: TTC single bit error counter bits[31:0]

Name: STATUS.TTC.SGL_BIT_ERRORS_HI
Description: TTC single bit error counter bits[47:32]

Name: STATUS.TTC.BCNT_ERRORS_HI
Description: bit 15-0 TTC BC0 error counter bits[47:32]

Name: STATUS.GENERAL.SYNC_LOST_TIME_LO
Description: L1A sync lost time counter bits[31:0]

Name: STATUS.GENERAL.SYNC_LOST_TIME_HI
Description: L1A sync lost time counter bits[47:32]

Name: STATUS.GENERAL.OF_WARN_TIME_LO
Description: L1A overflow warning time counter bits[31:0]

Name: STATUS.GENERAL.OF_WARN_TIME_HI
Description: L1A overflow warning time counter bits[47:32]

Name: STATUS.LDC.SFP0.NEXT_BUF
Description: Next monitor buffer for event builder 0

Name: STATUS.LDC.SFP1.NEXT_BUF
Description: Next monitor buffer for event builder 1

Name: STATUS.LDC.SFP2.NEXT_BUF
Description: Next monitor buffer for event builder 2

Name: STATUS.LDC.ALL.NEXT_BUF
Description: Next monitor buffer for all event builders

Name: STATUS.SFP0.ROM
Description: SFP0 ROM data(first 128 bytes, little endian)

Name: STATUS.SFP1.ROM
Description: SFP1 ROM data(first 128 bytes, little endian)

Name: STATUS.SFP2.ROM
Description: SFP2 ROM data(first 128 bytes, little endian)

Name: STATUS.TTC.ROM
Description: TTC/TTS SFP ROM data(first 128 bytes, little endian)

Name: FULL_MEMORY
Description: full memory read/write access. (write disabled in run mode) thru 0xfffffff
